            <p class="columns_2">
                
               <H2>Market Summary</H2>
<p>Eastgate Square is a single-level shopping centre located at the corner of Centennial Pkwy N. (Hwy. #20) and Queenston Rd. (Hwy. #8) in Stoney Creek/Hamilton, and is easily accessible from the Queen Elizabeth Way (QEW) and the local Red Hill Expressway. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>

<p>Anchored by Sears, Fortinos, Winners, HomeSense, and SportChek, Eastgate Square offers more than 100 stores and services including Dollarama, Kitchen Stuff Plus, Shoppers Drug Mart, and Urban Planet, and a free standing LCBO, The Beer Store, and Jack Astor&rsquo;s.</p>

<p>Eastgate Square is also home to a Hamilton Transit Facility with 8 different bus routes dropping customers off directly on the property.</p>

<p>In 2013, the centre completed a major re-development project, converting a former anchor tenant to additional common area and a number of mini-Anchors and Large Non-Majors. &nbsp;In 2015, the rest of the mall is being renovated to mirror the new finishes used in the 2013 renovation.</p>

<p>Eastgate Square&rsquo;s Primary Demographic consists of young families with children.</p>
               <br>
               <strong>Total GLA:  </strong><br>507,199 square feet <br><br>
               
               
              
         
          
